# 🧠 SkyCast — The Complete React Mental Model Guide

> **What this guide is:** A deep-dive into how to THINK like a React developer — applied to your SkyCast weather app. Zero code. Pure architecture, reasoning, and mental models.
>
> **Who this is for:** You — a beginner who has read the React docs up to "Passing Props" and is about to build their first real project.

