# PART 12 · Build Order (Leaves → Trunk)

## The Complete Sequence — What to Build and When

### 🟢 Phase 1: Foundation (Day 1 — first 2 hours)

| Step | What | Why This Order |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | Set up Vite project | You need a working development environment |
| 2 | Set up `index.css` with CSS variables + color palette | Every component will reference these colors |
| 3 | Build `StatCard` | Smallest, simplest component. Instant visual reward. |
| 4 | Build `ForecastRow` | Second smallest. Same idea. |

**Stop here and verify:** Do `StatCard` and `ForecastRow` look correct when you display one of each?

### 🟡 Phase 2: Containers (Day 1 — next 2 hours)

| Step | What | Why This Order |
|---|---|---|
| 5 | Build `StatsGrid` — render 6 `StatCard`s in a grid | You can now see if your grid layout works |
| 6 | Build `ForecastList` — render 7 `ForecastRow`s in a list | You can now see if your list scrolling works |
| 7 | Build `CurrentWeatherHero` — the big temperature card | Standalone card, no children needed |

**Stop here and verify:** Does the 3×2 grid look right? Does the scrollable list work?

### 🟠 Phase 3: Layout (Day 2)

| Step | What | Why This Order |
|---|---|---|
| 8 | Build `MainLayout` — two-column CSS Grid | This is just the skeleton — left/right split |
| 9 | Plug `StatsGrid`, `CurrentWeatherHero` into the left column | Left side starts looking like the design |
| 10 | Build `TabGroup` and `ForecastHeader` | The top of the right panel |
| 11 | Plug `ForecastHeader` and `ForecastList` into the right column | Right side now looks complete |
| 12 | Build `Navbar` with `SearchBar`, `BrandLogo`, etc. | Top bar across full width |

**Stop here and verify:** Does the full page layout match the screenshot? (All data is still fake.)

### 🔴 Phase 4: Interactivity (Day 3)

| Step | What | Why This Order |
|---|---|---|
| 13 | Add state for `activeTab` in `RightColumn` | Tabs now switch and highlight correctly |
| 14 | Show different forecast data based on active tab | Right side changes when you click tabs |
| 15 | Add state for search input in `SearchBar` | User can type in the search box |
| 16 | Add `ThemeToggle` state in `App` | Light/dark mode toggle |

### ⚫ Phase 5: Real Data (Day 4+)

| Step | What | Why This Order |
|---|---|---|
| 17 | Create `weatherApi.js` service file | Separate API logic from component logic |
| 18 | Add `isLoading` and `error` state in `App` | Handle the "waiting" and "failed" states |
| 19 | Connect search to real API calls | App now fetches real data on search |
| 20 | Handle loading spinner and error messages | User sees feedback while waiting |

### 🌟 Phase 6: Polish (Day 5+)

| Step | What |
|---|---|
| 21 | Build `SunMoonCard` with arc visualization (hardest visual element) |
| 22 | Fine-tune spacing, shadows, border-radius to match the screenshot |
| 23 | Add hover effects, transitions, subtle animations |
| 24 | Make it responsive for tablet and mobile |
| 25 | Add the gradient background matching the lavender design |

